<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">When LDON first came out, I was level 55 or so.  I think my record was like 17 wins 43 losses before they fixed some of the difficulty of the missions.  It was AWESOME!  Why?  Because when you won - it was a big deal.  It was hard to win and so winning was a real accomplishment.  
<br />

<br />
Now, the last LDONs I did were months ago.  They were hard guk missions and I was pulling, charming and slowing.  It was pretty rare that we lost, but not nearly as much fun.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
