<span class="name"><a name="84246"></a></span><span class="postdetails">#4:&nbsp;<font color=black><b></b> Author:&nbsp;<b>Nydara</b>,&nbsp;</font></span><span class="postdetails"><font color=black></font></span>
<a href="viewtopic.php?p=84246#84246"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails"><font color=black>Posted: Fri Nov 05, 2004 11:59 am</font><span class="gen"><br>
