<span class="postbody">Cease and Desist. Level 9 and 15 paladin stun spells, cost about 10 mana each, and are the absolute cornerstone of Paladin aggro. I had a paladin tank that once refused to cast the spell (he said they cost too much aggro). I told him that if he didn't use stuns to get aggro, I was leaving.
<br />

<br />
Moral of the story - he cast stun spells, we won, and there was much rejoicing.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
